Texts.Eng: Bring the ^green;Solar Panel^reset; to ^orange;me^reset; at the ^orange;Science Outpost^reset;
Now you've started the engineering path of your adventure. I suggest getting some other machines up soon!
Powered stations are a ^orange;huge productivity booster^white;. To start with, you'll need a ^orange;Solar Panel^reset; to produce energy. Build one on a ^orange;Power Station^reset;.
